@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ucueem(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.83 + v1 + 0.34)) + wp.cos(v2))
    v1 = wp.sin(0.67)
    v1 = (0.31 * v2)
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs(0.52))
    v0 = v1
    v0 = (v0 - v0)
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.91)) + (wp.cos(tmp + 0.37) / 0.92))
    tmp = wp.cos(v2)
    data[tid] = v0
